        <h2>Projects</h2>
        <div class="project">
            <img src="https://ars.els-cdn.com/content/image/1-s2.0-S2214212619306155-gr1.jpg">
            <h3>QR BASED PETROL PUMP</h3>
            <p>A QR-based petrol pump system revolutionizes the fueling process by integrating QR code technology into traditional petrol stations. Customers generate a unique QR code through a mobile app linked to their payment method. At the pump, they scan the QR code, initiating the fueling process without the need for physical cards or cash. The system securely verifies the transaction, authorizes fuel dispensing, and records the purchase. This innovation streamlines operations, reduces transaction time, and enhances security by minimizing the risk of card skimming and fraud. Additionally, it offers convenience to customers while paving the way for a cashless and contactless fueling experience.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="project">
            <img src="https://paytmblogcdn.paytm.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/09/WhatsApp-Image-2023-09-15-at-13.49.44.jpeg">
            <h3>A BLOCK CHAIN BASED RECORD SYSTEM</h3>
            <p> Blockchain-based Record System offers a decentralized and immutable platform for securely storing and managing records. Leveraging cryptographic techniques and distributed ledger technology, it ensures data integrity, transparency, and tamper resistance. Each transaction is recorded across a network of nodes, eliminating the need for a central authority. This system enhances trust and accountability in various sectors, including healthcare, finance, and supply chain management. With its transparent and auditable nature, Blockchain-based Record Systems provide a reliable solution for ensuring the integrity and authenticity of digital records, mitigating the risks associated with data manipulation and fraud.</p>
        </div>
